  {
   "id": "4a679316-c517-46ea-a676-3aa911030ff0",
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": "## 2. 데이터 불러오기",
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "id": "6368cf20-176d-40d1-be66-ec33f1d287eb",
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": "train = pd.read_csv('/kaggle/input/competitions/titanic/train.csv')\ntest = pd.read_csv('/kaggle/input/competitions/titanic/test.csv')\ngender_submission = pd.read_csv('/kaggle/input/competitions/titanic/gender_submission.csv')\n\nprint(\"train shape:\", train.shape)\nprint(\"test shape:\", test.shape)\n\n# train.head()",
